{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require people who run over cats to stop and to report it, and impose fine",
        "additional_details": "We believe that when someone hits a cat, they should get fined, because at the end of day it\u2019s someone\u2019s pet. I\u2019m doing this petition because my baby got run over and left in a bush for a nearly a week. I did not know he was gone I thought he was still missing.",
        "background": "We call on the Government to introduce a fine for people who run over cats as Owners have to pay vet bill no fault of their own. We think it\u2019s not right, and think a fine should be introduced even if it\u2019s only a \u00a350 fine",
